# UiSystem Module

## Overview

Responsive and Accessible Frontend

## Goals

- **G1** — Responsive and Accessible Frontend
- **G2** — Layout adapts to desktop, tablet, and mobile breakpoints
- **G3** — Keyboard shortcuts navigate between views without mouse
- **G4** — Focus management guides users through gate approval flows
- **G5** — Screen reader annotations describe node graph and relations
- **G6** — Theme & Accent Color System
- *...and 1 more*

## Key Architecture Decisions

- **A1** — Frontend Composable State Architecture
- **A2** — Search & Filter Architecture
- **A3** — Theme & Accent System Architecture

## Key Designs

- **D1** — Responsive 3-Zone Layout System
- **D2** — Theme & Accent Component System
- **D3** — SpecsView Layout Refactor

